Add Pulse Code Modulation Device Audio Interface support for MT8365 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Alexandre Mergnat <amergnat@baylibre.com>
---
 sound/soc/mediatek/mt8365/mt8365-dai-pcm.c | 293 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
